<h2>Hello <%= @participant.name %></h2>

This is a reminder that you are signed up for an experiment with the Humans and Automation Lab.

<h2>Time: <%= @slot.human_datetime %></h2>

<p>The experiment will last approximately <%= @experiment.human_time_length %><% if @experiment.compensation > 0 %> and you will be compensated $<%= @experiment.compensation %><%else%>, no compensation is provided<%end%> for your participation.</p>

<h2>Location: <a href="<%= @experiment.location.url %>"><%= @experiment.location.human_location %></a></h2>
<p><%= @experiment.location.directions %></p>

<b>Experiment Contact</b>
<p>Please contact <%= @experiment.user.name %> at <a href="mailto:<%= @experiment.user.email %>"><%= @experiment.user.email %></a> or <%= number_to_phone(@experiment.user.phone) %> if you have any questions.</p>